column2: SELECT TOP # S.ObjID, S.z, S.sn_#, #, L2.ew , L2.ewErr #, L3.ew, L3.ewErr FROM SpecPhoto AS S JOIN SpecObjAll AS sn ON S.SpecObjID = sn.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID WHERE L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (specclass = # or specclass = #) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
